            <div class="legend journal-contentLinkColor">Short summary</div>
            <div class="content hide-js shortSummaryFull">The data request of the Coupled Model Intercomparison Project Phase 6 (CMIP6) defines all the quantities
from CMIP6 simulations that should be archived. The building blocks and structure of the CMIP6 Data Request, which has been constructed to meet these challenges, are described in this paper.</div>
            <div style="display: none" class="content show-js shortSummaryShorten">The data request of the Coupled Model Intercomparison Project Phase 6 (CMIP6) defines all the...</div>
